(585723, ' [QUOTE=Luger_P08;260230]Mr. Patriot if you are that much Patriot then why are you asking illegal actions?\nI know you have the knowledge so donât try to judge our seniorâs knowledge, if you still insist that you donât have then follow these steps\nDecide the legal bore witch you want to buy  \nGet the license\nCheck the market \nAnd then buy the gun[/QUOTE]\n\nDear Luger, I felt sorry to read your reply. I didn''t think that one can go so ahead in suspicion. I didn''t know which bore is illegal that''s why I asked. Also, who damn think that I''m gonna having the gun without License. Always Think and say positive which reflects you own personality. Suspicion kills your image.', ''),
